Non-pharmacological solutions to sleep and circadian rhythm disruption: voiced 
bedside experiences of hospice and end-of-life staff caregivers.

Sagha Zadeh R(1), Capezuti E(2), Eshelman P(3), Woody N(4), Tiffany J(5), 
Krieger AC(6).

Author information:
(1)Health Design Innovations Lab (affiliated with Cornell's Institute for 
Healthy Futures), Design and Environmental Analysis, Cornell University, 2425 
Martha Van Rensselaer Hall, Ithaca, NY, 14853-4401, USA. rzadeh@cornell.edu.
(2)W.R. Hearst Foundation Chair in Gerontology, Hunter College of the City 
